data.description: Located on a cul-de-sac where you can relax and enjoy the lake view from your family room.  This home boasts many upgrades, including a beautiful updated kitchen in 2022, with stainless steel appliances and modern finishes. The home has updated flooring and paint throughout. The vaulted ceiling and skylight add to the feeling of openness.  The master bath was upgraded with a large shower and custom wood cabinetry.  There are accordion shutters and a whole house generator to ensure your comfort.  The garage is also wired for electric vehicle charging.  The roof is only 3 years old.  There is a monthly assessment fee of $215 for the roof.  It can also be paid in full at the time of closing if buyer chooses to do so.
